traits.name: Frozen
traits.description: An ice-covered world with frigid temperatures, providing unique research opportunities and resources such as ice water, ammonia ice, and other frozen compounds.

traits.name: Rocky
traits.description: A world with a rugged, rocky landscape, rich in minerals and other resources, providing a variety of opportunities for mining, research, and exploration.

traits.name: Barren
traits.description: A desolate world with little to no vegetation or water, presenting unique challenges for habitation and resource extraction.

traits.name: Jungle

traits.name: Temperate
traits.description: A world with a mild climate and balanced ecosystem, providing a comfortable environment for a variety of life forms and supporting diverse industries.

traits.name: Scattered Settlements
traits.description: A collection of dispersed communities, each independent yet connected through trade and communication networks.

traits.name: Marketplace
traits.description: A thriving center of commerce where traders from across the galaxy gather to buy, sell, and exchange goods.
